            <title>[LU-11777] interop: sanityn test 102 fails with &apos;check_fhandle_syscalls failed&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11777</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanityn test_102 was added to the Lustre test suites for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10337&quot; title=&quot;Open by handle does not work with unlinked files from multiple nodes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10337&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10337&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/30405/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/30405/&lt;/a&gt;. This test will fail for all Lustre servers with version less than 2.11.57. Thus, we need to add a version check to sanityn test 102.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
